title: Math Club!
text:
Activities (2024-2025)
We are planning regular biweekly meetings, some on Tuesday club hours, some on Thursday club hours. We have plans to host faculty talks.

title: About
text: The Math Club at College of Staten Island is a student activities club, registered with the Office of Student Life and funded by the student activity fee.

title: Past Events!
text: Each semester, the Math Club holds new and exciting events to get the student body involved in mathematics! Here is a past catalogue of our events: if you like what you see, come join us!
